name: Leaf Eater Simulator
description:
Become an (un)discerning cat as you try your best to eat every leaf in existence! Rumor has it of an ancient Elder Leaf in a space between worlds...see if you can find it!

Please provide feedback on this Google Form: https://forms.gle/bbiQCjk5ssDzG2tM9

Thank you in advance for helping make our game better!!
